Package jpigpio.sensors

Class GY_271

java.lang.Object
jpigpio.sensors.GY_271
public class GY_271
extends java.lang.Object
The GY-271 is a module that provides a multi axis magnetic field measurement that is typically used to provide a compass. It is based on the Honeywell HMC5883L IC. The module uses I2C for communications. This Java class provides a wrapper to its low level functions for use with Pigpio. author Neil Kolban date 2015-05-06
